OL,3,CBorder region misses out on 'Town of
OL,4,CCulture' shortlist
OL,6,FAppleby, Maryport, Kirkudbright, and
OL,7,FGalashiels were among those who bid to
OL,8,Fbecome the UK's 'Town of Culture 2028'
OL,9,Fand now miss out on #60,000.
OL,11,FFifteen towns have made the shortlist,
OL,12,Fselected from a list of almost 400
OL,13,Fapplications from across the country.
OL,15,FThe shortlisted towns are:
OL,17,FShortlisted towns will now receive
OL,18,F#60,000 each to develop their full
OL,19,Fbids, which will be assessed by the
OL,20,Findependent judging panel.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/3
