OL,3,CBorder region misses out on 'Town of
OL,4,CCulture' shortlist
OL,6,FOne finalist will then be selected
OL,7,Ffrom each category, with the overall
OL,8,Fwinner being announced early next year.
OL,10,FBids from our region:
OL,12,FThe UK Town of Culture competition is
OL,13,Fpart of the government's ambition to
OL,14,Frestore pride in local areas and
OL,15,Fdeliver a decade of national renewal,
OL,16,Ffollowing the announcement of the
OL,17,FPride in Place Programme last year.
