OL,3,CBorder region misses out on 'Town of
OL,4,CCulture' shortlist
OL,6,FOrganisers said: "Throughout this
OL,7,Fyear, this competition - together with
OL,8,Fthe UK City of Culture 2029
OL,9,Fcompetition - will continue to shine a
OL,10,Flight on local visions and voices from
OL,11,Facross the UK to help encourage
OL,12,Fincreased local investment, create a
OL,13,Flasting sense of pride, and open doors
OL,14,Fto the arts and culture for everyone."
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
